 &lt;td style="text-align: left">&lt;strong>Continuation&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">Turns into &lt;strong>Jugular Rip&lt;/strong>, &lt;strong>Abdomen Tear&lt;/strong>, or &lt;strong>Eye Gouge&lt;/strong> when under the effect of &lt;strong>Ready To Rip&lt;/strong>, &lt;strong>Ready To Tear&lt;/strong>, or &lt;strong>Ready To Gouge&lt;/strong> respectively. Also allows you to use &lt;strong>Hypervelocity/Fated Brand&lt;/strong> after &lt;strong>Burst Strike/Fated Circle&lt;/strong>.&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">
&lt;div class="md__image">
 &lt;img id="[9 55 34 81 412 432]" src="https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/img/jobs/tanks/gunbreaker/Jugular_Rip.png" onclick="openModal(this.id)" alt="JugularRip" />
&lt;/div>
&lt;/td>
